:: Forest Blood Gwylan Rescue
<<effects>>
You hear the trees rustle behind you. You slowly turn to look. Something digs at the back of your mind, as if surprised at the intrusion. It quickly turns to annoyance.
<br><br>

Someone emerges from the treeline. <span class="green">It's Gwylan.</span> <<nnpc_Hes "Gwylan">> wearing a green hooded cloak.
<br><br>

"There you are!
<<if $gwylan.timer.bloodVisit>>
	I got worried after you left the shop earlier."
<<elseif $gwylan.timer.bloodKnock>>
	I heard someone knocking at the shop, and I thought it might have been you."
<<else>>
	I thought I saw you shambling past the shop."
<</if>>
<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> looks you over, and steps closer. "Oh dear."
<br><br>

You stare at <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">>.
<br><br>

<span class="nextLink"><<link [[...|Forest Wraith Gwylan]]>><</link>></span>
<br>

:: Forest Blood Gwylan Rescue Repeat
<<effects>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
You hear the trees rustle behind you. You slowly turn to look. Something digs at the back of your mind, as if surprised at the intrusion. It quickly turns to annoyance.
<br><br>

Three green eyes stare from the shadows. A shape like a massive fox darts away, before reappearing somewhere else. It's all around you.
<br><br>

A branch breaks, and your body turns just in time to be tackled by something. <span class="green">It's Gwylan.</span>
<<if npcIsPregnant("Gwylan")>>
	Your body rolls with <<him>>, but throws <<him>> off. <<Hes>> sent reeling, but recovers quickly.
<<else>>
	Your body rolls with <<him>>, before kicking both of your legs into Gwylan's gut. <<Hes>> sent reeling, but recovers quickly.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Your body and Gwylan stare each other down. <<rainWraith>>
<br><br>

"I know you can hear me in there, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>. I'll do my best, but..." <<His>> voice trembles. "I won't be able to get you out by myself. I need you to fight it, however you can."
<br><br>

<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 4>>
	You feel like a fly trapped between two spiders.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

Gwylan runs towards you!
<br><br>

<span class="nextLink"><<link [[Fight|Wraith Snatched Gwylan Fight]]>><<set $fightstart to 1>><</link>></span>
