<<effects>><<set _notMoving to true>><<getTarget>>
<<set $nextPassage to "Forest Wraith Gwylan 3">>
Your body speaks.
<<if $willpowerSuccess>>
	<span class="green">Your voice cracks.</span>
<</if>>

"I'm well, Gwylan. I must have been sleepwalking. Thank you."
