<<He>> tilts <<his>> head, looking closer. "Sleepwalking. <<if $exposed gte 2>>Naked.<</if>> Right." <<He>> takes a step back.
"In that case, why not come by my shop? I have a remedy for sleepwalking<<if $exposed gte 2>>, and some warm clothes<</if>>."
