:: Forest Wraith Gwylan 4
<<effects>><<set _notMoving to true>><<getTarget>>
<<set $nextPassage to "Forest">>
<<if $willpowerSuccess>>
	<span class="green">You manage to let out a short, strained breath.</span>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

Your body speaks. "No, thank you. I prefer the solitude. It's a beautiful night."
<br><br>

<<He>> sighs. "Okay. Well... come see me tomorrow, then. I'm worried about you." <<He>> turns away, but pauses.
<br><br>

<<He>> walks back over to you, and hugs you tightly. Your body doesn't return it. "Your skin is very cold," <<he>> says. "Don't take long. I don't want you getting sick."
<span class="red"><<He>> turns, and leaves.</span>
<br><br>

<<endevent>><<set $gwylanDoesALittleTrolling to true>>

