:: Forest Wraith Gwylan 5
<<effects>><<getTarget>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<unset $nextPassage>>

You shamble through the forest. You know-
<br><br>

"Where are you going?" Your head throbs multiple times in quick succession upon hearing Gwylan's voice. "That isn't towards home. That's towards the lake."
<br><br>

You hear rapid footsteps, and <<he>> grabs you by the shoulders from behind. "I'm afraid I have to insist now. You're coming with me, back to the shop." <<He>> grabs your hand, and tries to pull you along.
<br><br>

You don't budge. You slowly turn to face <<him>>. The intruder in your body feels distant for a moment, as if thinking. It pulls against you, testing your will.
<br><br>

After a moment, <span class="green">you start to walk with <<him>></span>.
<br><br>

<span class="nextLink"><<link [[Follow. For now.|Forest Wraith Gwylan 6]]>><<set $phase2 to 1>><<pass 10>><</link>></span>
<br>

:: Forest Wraith Gwylan 6
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "forest_shop">><<effects>><<getTarget>><<set $nextPassage to "Forest Wraith Gwylan 7">>
"I've got a remedy that will make sure you sleep through the whole night. I wouldn't recommend drinking it more than twice a week though, unless you want regular sleep paralysis—"
<br><br>

Your body tunes Gwylan out. It does its best impression of normal walking. You feel strange. Almost as though it's going along with you, rather than you going along with it. <span class="purple">It's biding its time.</span>
<br><br>

You make it back to the forest shop with Gwylan. <<He>> leads you to a small table, before heading through a dark doorway.
<br><br>

Your eyes slowly move around the room, catching on a few of the knick-knacks around. "The gull's nest is empty," your body says. "You are all that remains."
<br><br>

"Sorry, what was that?" Gwylan's head pops out from the doorway. You stare at each other for a moment, saying nothing. <<He>> slowly ducks back into the other room.
<br><br>

You stare straight ahead for several minutes. The intruder's will pokes at yours. "<span class='wraith'>Fortunate, <<pcpetname "Wraith">>. Interference from the witch.</span>" You hear something like a laugh.
<<if $wraith.state is "haunt">>
	"<span class='wraith'>You will be pulled apart between us. Whom do you think is worse?</span>"
<<else>>
	"<span class='wraith'>Let us see which of us claims the fly from the web.</span>"
<</if>>
<br><br>

Gwylan returns holding a tray with a tea kettle. <<He>> pours hot water into a cup, and holds it in front of you.
"There you go!
<<if $gwylanTea gte 4>>
	Sorry that it isn't your favourite butterfly pea flower tea, but I think you'll enjoy it.
<</if>>
Drink it up." <<He>> pinches you on the cheek. You don't feel it. <<He>> sits on the opposite end of the table.
<br><br>

Your eyes look down at it. A <<wraithEyes>> tinge flashes over your vision, and your body feels sick looking at it.
<br><br>

<<link [[Drink it|Forest Shop]]>><</link>>
<br>
<span class="nextLink"><<link [[Do not.|Forest Wraith Gwylan 7]]>><</link>></span>
<br>

:: Forest Wraith Gwylan 7
