<<if $willpowerSuccess>>
	<span class="green">Your arm twitches.</span>
<</if>>
The teacup sits in front of you, untouched. Your body looks back up to Gwylan.
<br><br>

You stare at each other.
<br><br>

"Something wrong?" <<he>> says.<br>
"I'm not thirsty," your body says.<br>
"Ah, drank too much water?"<br>
Your head throbs.
<br><br>

You sit still.
<br><br>

<<link [[Drink it|Forest Shop]]>><</link>>
